flowRoot.flowPara: * An ActionScript 3 class for the SHA hash functions
// convert ByteArray to an array of uint

for (var i:uint=0; i<src.length; i+=4) { a.push(src.readUnsignedInt()); } var h:Array = core(a, len); var out:ByteArray = new ByteArray; var words:uint = getHashSize()/4; for (i=0; i<words; i++) { out.writeUnsignedInt(h[i]); }
